description	"Galak Fyyar

Class: Super Battle Droid
Brief Overview:
A large, tanky anti-Jedi class with an overshield that shocks and pushes away enemies.

^2Weaponry:
- Heavy Melee
-- 15% faster movement
- Repeater Arm Blaster (2)
-- Advanced Targeting [Sec. fire]
-- 20% less FP damage
-- Passive ammo regen
-- Alt. mode: Shoot blobs that knock down targets
--- High startup/cooldown/ammo drain 

^8Attributes:
- Prototype Cortosis Battle Armor
-- 50% Melee damage resist.
-- Cortosis (1)
-- Magnetic Plating
-- Blast Armor
-- Force Block (3)
-- Strength (2)
-- Healing (1)
-- Immune to Mind Trick (2)
- Large Personal Shield
-- Electrocutes/pushes enemies
-- Disabled when armor is depleted

^3Abilities:
- Battery Recharge (3) ^3[CS1]
-- Advanced Radar [Active during Recharge]
- Repulsor Wave (Force Push 1)

Galak Fyyar was a skilled commander and scientist of Desann's faction of the Imperial Remnant. He wore into battle a cortosis-based power armor of his own creation - equipped with a shield generator and mounted blaster cannon."